{"tid":411374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"比老母發現咗個condom","createTime":"2017-09-23T17:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T09:18:18.000Z","uid":140741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03b54d306d83b04a9d822d094c8a08964c1b8110","tid":411374,"uid":140741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T17:20:26.000Z","msg":"今日晏就男朋友上咗嚟 用淨咗一個condom <br />\n諗住陣間執 所以就咁放咗係床 <br />\n但之後同男朋友傾計同打機 就唔記得咗 淨係扔咗啲垃圾 <br />\n再後尾就出咗去食飯 頭先返到屋企就見到個condom被執放咗係書枱先醒起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n而老母又訓咗 11點半whatsapp佢又無咩特別反應 (都唔知佢幾時發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n究竟我依家收埋個condom定係由佢放係枱扮咩都唔知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n摸唔透我老母想我自首定佢扮無事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc8dfc5cc7b2d935eb82d3d6f038b4c2c1300c8","tid":411374,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T17:21:41.000Z","msg":"有咩問題"},{"pid":"a1f7207e35df228e1d46d846a000ee9c4d19f9b8","tid":411374,"uid":146092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T17:23:34.000Z","msg":"有用好過無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1954825e69dc0955b2df70c162d5f35129820999","tid":411374,"uid":21423,"like":9,"dislike":35,"score":-26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T17:23:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0164563cad04f3f1fe5a29714e4e0f5acabc645","tid":411374,"uid":140741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T17:26:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n其實我自己都覺得無咩問題 只係諗唔明佢放係枱係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同老母平時無乜幾句 唔會講心事"},{"pid":"0b624ee7004af8f3e1677c2e3424f24fbb86afcc","tid":411374,"uid":140741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0